source: TEXT_GAIUSA502_00754_SEQ_00<tab>Sister Kyokyozo of the Order of Nald'thal seeks an adventurer to slay creatures who are scaring away potential pilgrims to Thal's Respite.
target: TEXT_GAIUSA502_00754_SEQ_00<tab>ザルの祠の司祭キョキョゾは、冒険者に魔物の討伐を頼みたいようだ。

source: TEXT_GAIUSA502_00754_SEQ_01<tab>Pilgrims to Thal's Respite have grown scarce of late, and the vicious axe beaks who run rampant on the roads leading in are to blame. Slay four of the fearsome fowl.
target: TEXT_GAIUSA502_00754_SEQ_01<tab>付近の魔物を恐れ、巡礼者が減ってしまったらしい。ザルの祠周辺にいる「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2011901 /var>」を4匹討伐しよう。

source: TEXT_GAIUSA502_00754_SEQ_02<tab>You have slain four axe beaks, that would-be pilgrims might enter the hallowed halls of Thal's Respite without fear for their safety. Inform Sister Kyokyozo of your deeds.
target: TEXT_GAIUSA502_00754_SEQ_02<tab><var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2011901 /var>を4匹討伐した。ザルの祠の司祭「キョキョゾ」に報告しよう。

source: TEXT_GAIUSA502_00754_SEQ_03<tab>Sister Kyokyozo informs you that, thanks to your aid, she has already welcomed a traveling merchant and her family to the Respite. She looks forward to the many encounters with which the Traders will now bless her.
target: TEXT_GAIUSA502_00754_SEQ_03<tab>キョキョゾは、周囲の魔物が減って安心したようだ。これで巡礼者も安心してお参りができるだろう。

source: TEXT_GAIUSA502_00754_KYIKYOZO_000_000<tab>Adventurers, merchants, travelers─Thal's Respite is always open to those who seek a momentary reprieve from the hardships of the road.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA502_00754_KYIKYOZO_000_000<tab>この「ザルの祠」は、多くの巡礼者たちにとって
欠かせない巡礼地のひとつである、とても大切な場所。

source: TEXT_GAIUSA502_00754_KYIKYOZO_000_001<tab>In the past, we welcomed countless multitudes through these doors. Sadly, the growing presence of hostile beast tribes and savage creatures now deters many from making the pilgrimage. A shame, is it not?
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA502_00754_KYIKYOZO_000_001<tab>ですが、最近は増加する魔物や蛮族を恐れてか、
巡礼者の足が遠のいています。
……冒険者さん、お力を貸してはいただけませんか？

source: TEXT_GAIUSA502_00754_KYIKYOZO_000_002<tab>Perhaps you could come to our aid. The most fearsome of the local fauna is the axe beak. Were you to thin the flock─say, by four birds or so─I do believe these halls would be far more approachable.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA502_00754_KYIKYOZO_000_002<tab>せめて、この辺りだけでも安全に歩けるよう、
祠の周辺に生息する「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2011901 /var>」を
4匹ほど退治してほしいのです。

source: TEXT_GAIUSA502_00754_KYOKYOZO_000_020<tab>My adventuring friend, a traveling merchant and his family just walked through our doors not moments ago. Each encounter is a blessing─a blessing that would not have come to pass had those fearsome fowl continued to run rampant outside our halls. For this, I thank you.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA502_00754_KYOKYOZO_000_020<tab>冒険者さん、ありがとうございました。
これで巡礼者の方々も、安心してお参りできるでしょう。
